<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> الْحسن بن عَرَفَة وكناه.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١٨٩٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> مُعَاوِيَة بن هِشَام<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>الْقصار , الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سُفْيَان الثَّوْريّ , ومسعر.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
